resources.string: This app supports any android device having OS greater than android 2.2 (Froyo) API 8.
A3 provides a simple and efficient way to keep track of daily attendance and receive notifications in order to make user present on time.
# Set holidays and Leaves on Calander
# Can be used by any Faculty of NU
1. For the first time users have to register theirselves with their Name, ID No. and unique password to protect their account.
2. After registration user can login to his/her account and can view attaendance history, can receive notifications and set holidays and leaves on academic calendar.
3. Without registration or login, user can only able to see academic calendar of university.
4. For resolve any problem about the app user can contact help.
